translate spanish jezs8_d8ae786f:

    # det "No, but Javi keeps asking to get a dog."
    det "No, pero Javi no para de pedir un perro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:18
translate spanish jezs8_89e2d1b5:

    # det "I don't think he's mature enough to take care of one quite yet."
    det "No creo que sea lo suficientemente maduro para cuidar de uno todavía."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:20
translate spanish jezs8_edd444e9:

    # det "But I'll probably give in one of these days."
    det "Pero probablemente acabaré cediendo uno de estos días."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:21
translate spanish jezs8_b5107ad9:

    # det "I do like dogs."
    det "Me gustan los perros."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:23
translate spanish jezs8_2cd218b0:

    # det "I don't really have the time to take care of a pet though."
    det "Aunque la verdad es que no tengo tiempo para cuidar de una mascota."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:25
translate spanish jezs8_924b6ad9:

    # det "Or the energy."
    det "Ni energía."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:27
translate spanish jezs8_406113aa:

    # det "When I come home from work, I want to relax and spend some time with my family."
    det "Cuando llego a casa del trabajo, quiero relajarme y pasar tiempo con mi familia."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:29
translate spanish jezs8_12047b0c:

    # det "Not clean poop and pee out of the carpet."
    det "No limpiar caca y pis de la alfombra."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:31
translate spanish jezs8_19fa98ec:

    # det "And Mamá would not want to deal with that, for sure."
    det "Y a mamá no le gustaría lidiar con eso, seguro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:32
translate spanish jezs8_f8db6c17:

    # det "She doesn't even like dogs. Wouldn't ever let me have one, growing up."
    det "Ni siquiera le gustan los perros. Nunca me dejó tener uno cuando era pequeño."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:34
translate spanish jezs8_ebf5e8f6:

    # det "But Javi is getting to that age where he wants a pet or a brother or something."
    det "Pero Javi está llegando a esa edad en la que quiere una mascota, un hermano o algo así."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:36
translate spanish jezs8_7132ad21:

    # det "And I want him to have something besides playing Minecraft online with his friends."
    det "Y yo quiero que tenga algo más que jugar al Minecraft online con sus amigos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:38
translate spanish jezs8_f8f25e06:

    # det "So yeah, no pets yet, but probably gonna get a dog soon for Javi."
    det "Así que sí, todavía no tenemos mascotas, pero probablemente pronto tendremos un perro para Javi."

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezs8.rpy:40
translate spanish jezs8_baf48f07:

    # det "That will be... interesting."
    det "Eso va a ser... interesante."

